      "2do puesto: Rincón Salsero by Yénier Jiménez (Costa Rica)",
      "3er puesto: Alma Dance Company by Alessandro Massaro (Italia)",
    ],
  },
  {
    title: "Grupos Bachata",
    image: "grupo-bachata-2024.jpg",
    podium: [
